          <h3 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px;">What is GlamourBeauty's return policy?</h3>
          <p style="opacity: 0.8; font-size: 16px;">We accept returns within 30 days of purchase for unused products in their original packaging. Please check our full Return Policy page for more details.</p>
